query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(q1 t1 tq1 u1) NoHashJoin(q1 s t1 tq1 u1 a1) */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 1 AND q1.favorite_count <= 10
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('14.04',
'16.04',
'18.04',
'apex',
'boot',
'etymology',
'kernel',
'lightning-aura-components',
'networking',
'nouns',
'phrase-requests',
'single-word-requests',
'word-usage')
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 10 AND u1.upvotes <= 1000000
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = u1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('apple',
'askubuntu',
'english',
'salesforce')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND a1.question_id = q1.id group by t1.name;
